snippet.title: Goldenheart - Game Trailer
snippet.description: You have entered a foreign land in the course of an expedition and become unintentionally involved in an otherworldly mystery. Tuldenorrea is a deceptively simple world, balanced delicately between the extreme forces of a magical universe.
